I know this is going to be a silly review but if you love hot, soft pretzels then you MUST have one from here.
They are sooooooooooooooooo good!
They are big, soft, buttery and delicious.
I had no idea I could get such a delicious pretzel at a gas station.
So, go try one so you can see why I am so adamant about them.
