They finally have a store in Buckeye.
Very large and clean store.
The staff are friendly and the area that it is in is heavily patrolled by Buckeye PD, MCSO, and DPS.
This is probably one of the safest gas stops heading out west towards the California border.
I hope they build a QT in Quartzsite.
That would be really nice.

